  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><div><b>“</b><span>For kabobs, perhaps?</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a></p>\n</div>\n<p><b>Inedible</b> is one of the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Value\" title=\"Food Value\">Food Value</a> that can be used to cook in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a>. Many Crock Pot recipes have restrictions on the amount of Inedible items they accept, while some require a specific Inedible item as ingredient.\n</p>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dorsal_Fin\" title=\"Dorsal Fin\"><img alt=\"Dorsal Fin\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dorsal_Fin.png?a8602e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dorsal_Fin\" title=\"Dorsal Fin\">Dorsal Fin</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Weevole_Carapace\" title=\"Weevole Carapace\"><img alt=\"Weevole Carapace\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Weevole_Carapace.png?d00643\" width=\"64\" height=\"64